Linkage disequilibrium (LD) patterns were visualized using LDmatrix (LDlink, NIH) based on 1000 Genomes Phase 3 reference panels. Pairwise LD was quantified using r\'b2 to assess tagging relationships between variants. For selected loci, LD matrices were constructed separately for East Asian (EAS) and European (EUR) populations using identical sets of variants centered on the lead edQTL SNP (\'b1100 kb).\
